It is expected that whoever wins the rights will have to put at least £12 million into the financial pot for the richest fight of all time.

Sky are having to consider pushing their pay-per-view charge above their notional £20 barrier.

Warren is believed to be offering an innovative package for his monthly subscription network which could raise the ante higher.

 

